---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../styles/services/payroll.css";
---

<Layout>
  <main class="service-page payroll-page">
    <section class="service-page-hero">
      <div class="service-page-shell">
        <p class="service-page-eyebrow">payroll</p>
        <h1>The right platform, properly connected.</h1>
        <p class="service-page-lead">
          We help clients select, configure, and connect payroll systems so
          payroll information flows correctly into the accounting and tax
          process.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="service-page-intro">
      <div class="service-page-shell service-page-two-column">
        <div>
          <p class="service-page-kicker">How we help</p>
          <h2>Payroll support without forcing one system</h2>
        </div>
        <p>
          Payroll platforms have improved, but setup still matters. A good
          system should calculate payroll correctly, file required returns,
          integrate with the general ledger, and give the business owner clear
          access to reports. We help make those pieces work together.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="service-page-offerings">
      <div class="service-page-shell">
        <div class="service-page-section-heading">
          <p class="service-page-kicker">Services</p>
          <h2>Support built around what you need.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="service-page-grid">
          <article class="service-page-offering">
            <h3>Platform selection</h3>
            <p>
              Evaluation of payroll providers based on business size,
              complexity, integrations, and support needs.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="service-page-offering">
            <h3>Implementation and setup</h3>
            <p>
              Assistance configuring accounts, payroll items, tax settings, and
              the accounting connection.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="service-page-offering">
            <h3>QuickBooks Online integration</h3>
            <p>
              Review of payroll journal entries and mapping so payroll posts
              consistently to the correct accounts.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="service-page-offering">
            <h3>Ongoing coordination</h3>
            <p>
              Help interpreting reports, resolving accounting issues, and
              communicating with the payroll provider when problems arise.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="service-page-questions">
      <div class="service-page-shell service-page-two-column">
        <div>
          <p class="service-page-kicker">Common questions</p>
          <h2>Start with the question in front of you.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="service-page-question-list">
          <article class="service-page-question">
            <h3>Do you run payroll for clients?</h3>
            <p>
              No. We work with established payroll platforms and help clients
              choose and implement the right one.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="service-page-question">
            <h3>Can you help connect payroll to QuickBooks?</h3>
            <p>
              Yes. We review the integration and account mapping so payroll
              activity is recorded properly.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="service-page-question">
            <h3>Can you help if the current setup is wrong?</h3>
            <p>
              Yes. We can review the payroll reports, accounting entries, and
              provider settings to identify where the process is breaking down.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="service-page-cta">
      <div class="service-page-shell service-page-cta-inner">
        <div>
          <p class="service-page-kicker">Let's talk</p>
          <h2>Need help with payroll?</h2>
          <p>
            Tell us what you are working through. We will help you determine the
            next practical step.
          </p>
        </div>
        <a href="/contact">Contact Us</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
